Class QRCodeEncoder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.zxing.client.android.encode.QRCodeEncoder

  • public final class QRCodeEncoder
extends Object
    This class does the work of decoding the user's request and extracting all the data to be encoded in a barcode.
